# Generated by /usr/bin/select-editor
#SELECTED_EDITOR="/bin/ed"
SELECTED_EDITOR="/usr/bin/gedit"

(or)

The crontab -e command will check the environment variables $EDITOR and $VISUAL

$export EDITOR=gedit
or
$export VISUAL=gedit

To make it permanent, add in .bashrc or .bash_profile
